{"type": "article", "id": 11347, "title": "Bibi Lab游牧行李箱", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-29T11:12:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016070215423047y3ukVFvadsXKrE.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t日本家具品牌 Bibi Lab 最近推出了一款新品行李箱 Nomad Suitcase，可谓是游牧工作者的福音。除了拥有与一般大型行李箱一样的储存空间外，还可以变身为流动写字桌，箱子一旁还设有折合式的椅子，适合旅行、出差等各种外出需要桌椅的场合使用。这款游牧行李箱净重仅为 7.15 kg ，若是把桌椅装置拆除的话，仅为 4.86 kg。售价 312 美元（约合人民币 1938 元），<a href=\"http://www.japantrendshop.com/nomad-suitcase-p-2939.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154227tmQdbGAjikvEOoWF.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"352\" title=\"a\" alt=\"a\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154227zf0nSURmMIwvh1DE.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"330\" title=\"a\" alt=\"a\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016070215422868BTcuSG7MkgbaVH.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"212\" title=\"a\" alt=\"a\" data-ratio=\"0.35333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154228jb6QEWyTpVF5rt8C.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"212\" title=\"a\" alt=\"a\" data-ratio=\"0.35333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154229HG5anjsqokp3zZJS.jpg\" width=\"736\" height=\"520\" title=\"a\" alt=\"a\" data-ratio=\"0.70652174\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n"}